Race.SpecificTitle: PW Fantasy Sports -- Authorize Fantasy Sports Contests - Act 322, 2018
Race.SummaryText: PROPOSITION TO AUTHORIZE FANTASY SPORTS CONTESTS.
Race.FullText: Shall fantasy sports contests be permitted in the parish of Morehouse?

Race.SpecificTitle: Bastrop Area Fire Protection Dist. No. 2 -- 6.70 Mills Continuation - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Bastrop Area Fire Protection District No. 2 Proposition
(Millage Continuation)
Race.FullText: Shall Bastrop Area Fire Protection District No. 2 of the Parish of Morehouse, State of Louisiana (the "District"), under the authority of Article VI, Sections 30 and 32 of the Constitution of the State of Louisiana of 1974, and other constitutional and statutory authority, continue to levy and collect a special tax of six and seventy hundredths (6.70) mills, which is the rate previously authorized at an election held in the District on April 4, 2009, on all the property subject to taxation in the District, for an additional period of ten (10) years beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, inclusive, for the purpose of constructing, purchasing, maintaining and operating fire protection equipment and facilities, title to which shall be in the public, and paying fire department salaries (estimated annual revenues: $258,900)?

Race.SpecificTitle: 10th Ward Fire Protection District No. 1 -- 3.95 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
10th Ward Fire Protection District No. 1 Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall 10th Ward Fire Protection District No. 1 of the Parish of Morehouse, State of Louisiana (the "District"), under the provisions of Article VI, Sections 30 and 32 of the Constitution of the State of Louisiana of 1974, and other constitutional and statutory authority, continue to levy and collect a special tax of three and ninety-five hundredths (3.95) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District, for an additional period of ten (10) years beginning with the year 2019 and ending with the year 2028, inclusive, to pay for the supervision, operation and maintenance of said fire protection district, and to acquire, maintain and operate fire protection equipment vehicles and equipment (estimated annual revenues: $37,000)?
